                    We care 100% about all users privacy, and maintain all the software updates.
                    <br />
                    The decentralized nature of the Bitcoin network allows for a highly resilient value transfer infrastructure, and this allows merchants to save money, This is because there are little to no fees for transferring Bitcoins from one person to another. Unlike other payment methods, Bitcoin payments cannot be reversed, so once you are paid you can ship! No waiting days for a payment to clear. You can also choose BTCPay Server as a self-hosted solution on your own server.
                    <br />
